y_birthday_lobste_rs\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e2016\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/s/mazaum/happy_5th_anniversary_lobsters\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e2017\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/s/cgtc2w/happy_7th_anniversary_lobsters\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e2019\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/s/orrpdv/lobsters_launched_8_years_ago_today\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e2020\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/s/idj3tm/lobsters_is_nine_today\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e2021\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/s/jclvos/one_decade_lobsters\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e2022\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/s/hhoopi/lobsters_is_11_today\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e2023\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/s/slfdci/one_dozen_lobsters\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e2024\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/s/8we4dn/lucky_13_lobsters\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e2025\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLook back at the last year’s \u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/top/1y\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003etop stories\u003c/a\u003e,\nor review your upvoted \u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/upvoted/comments\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003ecomments\u003c/a\u003e\nand \u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/upvoted/stories\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003estories\u003c/a\u003e to share your favorites.\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"Hey folks,\r\n\r\nOnce more around the sun, today is 14 years since Lobsters launched in 2012.\r\n\r\nLike the the [American fourteeners](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fourteener), our [activity charts](https://lobste.rs/stats) have been busily sloping upwards.\r\nWe now have 20,412 users who've submitted 127,589 stories, written 696,054 comments, and cast 4,911,743 votes.\r\n(I'm happy to run [more complicated queries](https://lobste.rs/about#queries) than `count(*)`.)\r\n\r\n\r\nPreviously:\r\n[2013](https://lobste.rs/s/rxmopc/lobsters_is_1_year_old_today)\r\n[2016](https://lobste.rs/s/9fcuzc/happy_birthday_lobste_rs)\r\n[2017](https://lobste.rs/s/mazaum/happy_5th_an